## 9. ConvenГ§Гµes de Nomenclatura

| Tipo                     | ConvenГ§ГЈo               | Exemplo                        |
|--------------------------|-------------------------|--------------------------------|
| Componentes React        | PascalCase              | `UserCard.tsx`                 |
| Arquivos de utilitГЎrio   | kebab-case              | `format-date.ts`               |
| Hooks                    | camelCase com `use`     | `useAuth.ts`                   |
| Server Actions           | camelCase com `Action`  | `createUserAction.ts`          |
| Loaders                  | camelCase com `Loader`  | `dashboard.loader.ts`          |
| Schemas Zod              | camelCase com `Schema`  | `user.schema.ts`               |
| Services                 | camelCase com `Service` | `user.service.ts`              |
| Tipos/Interfaces         | PascalCase              | `UserProfile`, `ApiResponse`   |
| Pastas de rota           | kebab-case              | `user-settings/`               |
| Pastas privadas          | underscore prefix       | `_components/`, `_lib/`        |
| Route Groups             | parentheses             | `(auth)/`, `(dashboard)/`      |

